text: Victor Scvortov (born March 30, 1988) is a Moldovan-born Emirati judoka. He originally represented his birth nation in international events, but he moved to the United Arab Emirates along with two other Moldovan judoka in 2013. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 73 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the third round by Shohei Ono. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Moldovan male judoka Category:Emirati male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of the United Arab Emirates Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Judoka at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for the United Arab Emirates Category:Asian Games medalists in judo Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games
